OL,3,CMan, 51, jailed for 28 years for
OL,4,Cgrooming six young girls on Snapchat
OL,6,FA 51-year-old man has been sentenced
OL,7,Fto 28 years in jail after pleading
OL,8,Fguilty to 34 sexual offences against
OL,9,Fsix girls he met on the social media
OL,10,Fapp Snapchat.
OL,12,FPaul Lipscombe, who was sentenced at
OL,13,FLeicester Crown Court today, met up
OL,14,Fwith five of the girls and committed
OL,15,Fmultiple sexual offences between
OL,16,FSeptember 2023 and April 2024.
OL,18,FThe victims were aged between 12 and
OL,19,F15 at the time and are from across the
OL,20,FUK.
